updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"举例论证（典型事例）"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"     ：选取古今中外典型人物或时事热点，通过具体故事来支撑论点，做到叙议结合，拒绝单纯堆砌素材。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-2fqdllz","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-2fqdllz","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-o248573","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-o248573","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"归谬论证（反向推导）"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"     ：先提出与论点相反的假定，推导出荒谬或不可接受的后果，从而有力地反证原论点的正确性，增强说服力。"}]}]}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-l85ss3s","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-l85ss3s","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-6isog05","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-6isog05","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"辅助论式拓展"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"：可适当穿插使用道理/引证论证（引用经典著作、名人警句）、类比论证（通过相似事物比较类推）或反证法，丰富文章的论证维度。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-rdktf5d","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-rdktf5d","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-4assta4","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-4assta4","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"隐性植入辩证法"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"：将辩证法的三大规律(对立同一、量变质变、否定之否定)内化为文章的底层逻辑，但"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"严禁直接出现"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"“对立统一”、“量变质变”、“否定之否定”等哲学术语。具体操作如下："}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-bp9hmnk","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-bp9hmnk","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-mt0mow3","Type":"NodeLis