","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-u0vevie","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"核心素材优先库："}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-s8d4hr2","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-s8d4hr2","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-obtt52i","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-obtt52i","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-t3owxou","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-t3owxou","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"钱伟长（中国力学之父）：必须作为核心论据或升华点。重点使用其“九一八事变后，物理仅15分的他毅然弃文从理，只为‘科学救国’”的转折。体现“个人命运与国家命运的同频共振”，以此替换老旧的“范仲淹”、“岳飞”等素材。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-7ex5cwd","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-7ex5cwd","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-krm9nzv","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-krm9nzv","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"西西弗斯（加缪笔下的荒诞英雄）：必须作为核心意象。重点描写他推石上山的徒劳与坚持，引用“登上顶峰的斗争本身足以充实人的心灵”。用以论证“在无意义的生活中构建意义”、“过程即意义”，以此替换老旧的“海伦·凯勒”、“张海迪”等素材。"}]}]}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-79unfid","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Delimiter":46,"Marker":"Ny4=","Num":7},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-79unfid","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-ayyqffh","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-ayyqffh","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"古典底蕴与化用："}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-rjmldt0","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-rjmldt0","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-op9q48b","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-op9q48b","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-czwtyn9","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-czwtyn9","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"至少自然嵌入2–3条下面提供的的典故、文章(不必引用原文，文章总结、提炼亦可)、诗词名句、电影，并保证与论证逻辑紧密相关。在保证与论证逻辑紧密相关的情况下，优先使用标记为(优先)的条目。"}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-jxhqed2","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-jxhqed2","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-xgsvkgx","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-xgsvkgx","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-o1sbq7w","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-o1sbq7w","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"《尚书》五福：寿、福、康宁、攸好德、考终命(优先)"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-8zqxoas","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-8zqxoas","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-ql1lzuv","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-ql1lzuv","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"鲁迅：无穷的远方，无数的人们，都与我相关。(优先)"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-79vnj8d","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-79vnj8d","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-5oq3cwl","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-5oq3cwl","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"罗曼·罗兰：世界上只有一种英雄主义，就是在认清生活的真相之后依然热爱生活。(优先)"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-ha4nqxx","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-ha4nqxx","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-nry4xvy","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-nry4xvy","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"特鲁多医生墓志铭：医生有时治愈，常常帮助，总是安慰。(优先)"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-g5yhe1c","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-g5yhe1c","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-bn5k5q7","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-bn5k5q7","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"罗素：参差多态乃是人类幸福的本源。(优先)"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-ermjllc","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-ermjllc","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-zz81fku","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-zz81fku","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"尼采：每一个不曾起舞的日子都是对生命的辜负。(优先)"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-cmcn4qi","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-cmcn4qi","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-9dgvimg","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-9dgvimg","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"投之亡地然后存，陷之死地然后生。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-sxo0596","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-sxo0596","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-kal37ju","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-kal37ju","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"赏不逾日，罚不还面。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-xr3n58i","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-xr3n58i","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-hzan6db","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-hzan6db","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"路遥《平凡的世界》当一个人集中地凝视着自己的不幸时，他就很难想象别人的苦难。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-9eh957t","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-9eh957t","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-p5i1tjs","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-p5i1tjs","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"小敌之坚，大敌之擒也。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-c2nsz0t","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-c2nsz0t","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-rakgxmp","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-rakgxmp","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"小人肥口，君子肥身。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-hz3dp84","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-hz3dp84","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-5q2lqh1","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-5q2lqh1","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"我生本无乡，心安是归处。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-cfgj4l3","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-cfgj4l3","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-1xgd4iu","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-1xgd4iu","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"陈独秀：青春如初春，如朝日，如百卉之萌动，如利刃之新发于硎(xíng)，人生最宝贵之时期也。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-zhk8jri","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-zhk8jri","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-pothbt7","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-pothbt7","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"舒婷《致橡树》：我们分担寒潮、风雷、霹雳；我们共享雾霭流岚、虹霓。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-t750nlr","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-t750nlr","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-8ajzcr8","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-8ajzcr8","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"《美丽心灵》约翰·纳什"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-hejeo0v","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-hejeo0v","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-f3ulf19","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-f3ulf19","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"西格里夫·萨松：心有猛虎，细嗅蔷薇。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-bdl0xyp","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-bdl0xyp","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-ehpvxa6","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-ehpvxa6","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"歌德：大胆的见解就好比下棋时移动一个棋子，它可能被吃掉，但它却是胜局的起点。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-aljxgxs","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-aljxgxs","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-ji4etbt","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-ji4etbt","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"加缪：西西弗斯无声的全部快乐就在于：他的命运是属于他的，他的岩石是他的事情。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-c3tit4g","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-c3tit4g","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-ccu42rh","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-ccu42rh","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"加缪：在隆冬，我终于知道，我身上有一个不可战胜的夏天。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-6ekkh6j","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-6ekkh6j","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-5puva3y","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-5puva3y","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"海明威：一个人可以被毁灭，但不能被打败。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-r3q1emz","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-r3q1emz","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-8pgpehf","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-8pgpehf","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"杨绛：生活一半是柴米油盐，一半是星辰大海。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-veveckd","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-veveckd","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-y0kmdxy","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-y0kmdxy","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"昭昭若日月之明，离离如星辰之行。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-8g31yme","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-8g31yme","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-36xbxun","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-36xbxun","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"事以急败，思因缓得。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-ekcybx0","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-ekcybx0","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-su4hmlz","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-su4hmlz","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"晚来风定钓丝闲，上下是新月。千里水天一色，看孤鸿明灭。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-eazfxe0","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-eazfxe0","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-6f22i6u","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-6f22i6u","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"老舍《骆驼祥子》：经验是生活的肥料，有什么样的经验便变成什么样的人，在沙漠里养不出牡丹来。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-jlrob36","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-jlrob36","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-kc4yt5o","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-kc4yt5o","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"黄金累千，不如一贤。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-n8xjg2p","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-n8xjg2p","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-f7areg5","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-f7areg5","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"歌德：理论是灰色的，唯生命之树常青。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-mh6l989","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-mh6l989","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-946ao51","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-946ao51","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"道不同，不相为谋。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-qz7n361","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-qz7n361","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-9ckkkew","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-9ckkkew","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"浴不必江海，要之去垢；马不必骐骥，要之善走。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-jr52yjw","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-jr52yjw","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-nyh04dq","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-nyh04dq","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"苟利于民不必法古，苟周于事不必循旧。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-bxi30t1","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-bxi30t1","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-k0mk7b1","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-k0mk7b1","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"怀重宝者，不以夜行；任大功者，不以轻敌。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-7xkqgwq","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-7xkqgwq","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-442yeft","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-442yeft","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"独行穿落叶，闲坐数流萤。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-96bzagr","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-96bzagr","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-d1iclq1","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-d1iclq1","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"佯北勿从，锐卒勿攻，饵兵勿食。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-f41ict7","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-f41ict7","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-kn6vgit","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-kn6vgit","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"泰戈尔：只有流过血的手指，才能弹出世间的绝唱。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-lt3tt6j","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-lt3tt6j","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-gvmxwzu","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-gvmxwzu","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"《蛤蟆先生去看心理医生》：没有一种批判比自我批判更强烈，也没有一个法官比我们自己更严苛。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-a9ttokc","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-a9ttokc","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-wzip9f1","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-wzip9f1","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"德不孤，必有邻。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-2wz9b79","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-2wz9b79","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-j1p66ex","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-j1p66ex","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"吹灭读书灯，一身都是月。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-ijutlv7","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-ijutlv7","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-7ma0q1f","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-7ma0q1f","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"古今之成大事业、大学问者，必经过三种之境界：“昨夜西风凋碧树，独上高楼，望尽天涯路”，此第一境也；“衣带渐宽终不悔，为伊消得人憔悴”，此第二境也；“众里寻他千百度，蓦然回首，那人却在灯火阑珊处”，此第三境也。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-lvnh23u","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-lvnh23u","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-nv8rja0","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-nv8rja0","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"勿以身贵而贱人，勿以独见而违众。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-44r6a32","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-44r6a32","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-bpile0b","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-bpile0b","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"山河虽无恙，吾辈当自强。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-lmcpd76","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-lmcpd76","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-vxabvm1","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-vxabvm1","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"君埋泉下泥销骨，我寄人间雪满头。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-oiy8ps0","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-oiy8ps0","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-8ogt02k","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-8ogt02k","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"蛇蛇硕言，出自口矣。巧言如簧，颜之厚矣。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-9ph7sub","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-9ph7sub","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-ck7wg9q","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-ck7wg9q","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"良剑期乎断，不期乎镆铘；良马期乎千里，不期乎骥骜(jì ào)。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-w6ote5l","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-w6ote5l","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-u8lg4dl","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-u8lg4dl","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"勤能补拙，学可医愚。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-p0y5nke","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-p0y5nke","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-dyjmeme","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-dyjmeme","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"男儿何不带吴钩，收取关山五十州。请君暂上凌烟阁，若个书生万户侯？"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-kwzuviq","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-kwzuviq","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-s2kxz08","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-s2kxz08","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"为政不难，不得罪于巨室。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-k25bip8","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-k25bip8","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-gq0q7l6","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-gq0q7l6","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"长恨人心不如水，等闲平地起波澜。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-kmiwfpu","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-kmiwfpu","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-mkh9uti","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-mkh9uti","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"试玉要烧三日满，辨材须待七年期。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-9oaho2m","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-9oaho2m","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-pjjqtvh","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-pjjqtvh","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"清风一枕南窗卧，闲阅床头几卷书。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-x42a8lt","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-x42a8lt","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-cke8ine","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-cke8ine","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"不知而自以为知，百祸之宗也。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-4bpvo1k","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-4bpvo1k","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-veqg3fi","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-veqg3fi","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"轻财足以聚人，律己足以服人，量宽足以得人，身先足以率人。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-p8g11gt","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-p8g11gt","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-oq0o3zb","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-oq0o3zb","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"百战百胜，不如一忍。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-oqna5gc","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-oqna5gc","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-ukwi3u9","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-ukwi3u9","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"功名半纸，风雪千山。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-tvfwmx5","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-tvfwmx5","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-bv4625r","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-bv4625r","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"井以甘竭，李以苦成。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-w2wc98m","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-w2wc98m","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-eprsa7q","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-eprsa7q","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"赠君明月满前溪，直到西湖畔。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-6iikdf8","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-6iikdf8","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-s6yjcci","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-s6yjcci","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"道虽迩(ěr)，不行不至；事虽小，不为不成。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-ck4mudp","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-ck4mudp","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-w7lwduq","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-w7lwduq","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"为草当作兰，为木当作松。兰秋香风远，松寒不改容。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-rm1yef3","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-rm1yef3","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-30u2hpn","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-30u2hpn","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"善用威者不轻怒，善用恩者不妄施。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-ohs262y","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-ohs262y","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-tmifcd1","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-tmifcd1","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"马先驯而后求良，人先信而后求能。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-83ypf44","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-83ypf44","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-zxfs4wz","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-zxfs4wz","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"形象水，水之形，避高而趋下，兵之形，避实而击虚。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-aln7prf","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-aln7prf","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-5ahks6j","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-5ahks6j","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"人要是不能从过程中体味幸福和快乐，生命就成了一场荒诞的苦役。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-1zt5d16","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-1zt5d16","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-4yykwqh","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-4yykwqh","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"君王城上竖降旗，妾在深宫那得知？十四万人齐解甲，更无一个是男儿！"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-u7tb4hn","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-u7tb4hn","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-jym9ha7","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-jym9ha7","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"善用兵者，避其锐气，击其惰归，此治气者也。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-el3romi","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-el3romi","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-gva3db9","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-gva3db9","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"政入万山围子里，一山放出一山拦。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-aiosuwx","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-aiosuwx","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-5t7fofk","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-5t7fofk","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"天地者万物之逆旅也；光阴者百代之过客也。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-3p23m46","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-3p23m46","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-hfujrmg","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-hfujrmg","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"虽不能至，心向往之。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-j52h2ox","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-j52h2ox","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-2olbvy0","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-2olbvy0","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"高者未必贤，下者未必愚。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-cndm77n","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-cndm77n","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-hm36yeu","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-hm36yeu","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"与朋友交游，须将他们好处留心学来，方能受益；对圣贤言语，必要我平时照样行去，才算读书。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-vdjoe93","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-vdjoe93","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-5b3flb7","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-5b3flb7","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"二人同心，其利断金；同心之言，其臭(xiù)如兰。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-h0vdg1d","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-h0vdg1d","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-fenw26l","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-fenw26l","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"君子不蔽人之美，不言人之恶。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-5o5f56h","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-5o5f56h","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-jb1e99l","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-jb1e99l","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"知者不怨人，知命者不怨天；怨人者穷，怨天者无志。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-xtbpbcs","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-xtbpbcs","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-n0dqu2q","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-n0dqu2q","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"道德用于自律时好过一切法律，用于律他时坏过一切私刑！"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-ojdyg9q","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-ojdyg9q","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-iht1rs9","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-iht1rs9","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"山高自有客行路，水深自有渡船人。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-jly54hy","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-jly54hy","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-zd5eq1p","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-zd5eq1p","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"攻人以谋不以力，用兵斗智不斗多。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-xqi3g92","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-xqi3g92","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-bmb3jft","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-bmb3jft","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"不忘初心，方得始终。初心易得，始终难守。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-tfuqlkx","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-tfuqlkx","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-9hnohcl","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-9hnohcl","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"不迁怒，不贰过。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-cvjmk4c","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-cvjmk4c","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-rmpgmmn","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-rmpgmmn","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"用兵之法，十则围之，五则攻之，倍则分之，敌则能战之，少则能逃之，不若则能避之。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-2fe9rgt","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-2fe9rgt","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-hhezpcb","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-hhezpcb","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"越自尊大，越见器小。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-aw594ui","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-aw594ui","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-p3swukh","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-p3swukh","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"浮云一别后，流水十年间。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-yc8mqm8","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-yc8mqm8","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-hiwkzlf","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-hiwkzlf","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"穆勒 ：个人的自由，以不侵犯他人的自由为自由。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-81rbxa0","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-81rbxa0","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-bjnrs1u","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-bjnrs1u","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"小舟从此逝，江海寄余生。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-2msftmq","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-2msftmq","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-7nar1zo","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-7nar1zo","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"云山苍苍，江水泱泱，先生之风，山高水长！"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-s5mmcnp","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-s5mmcnp","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-m7f6pep","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-m7f6pep","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"行远道者假于车，济江海者因于舟。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-z04h6j5","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-z04h6j5","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-2e4rmk4","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-2e4rmk4","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"一花独放不是春，百花齐放春满园。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-x81zgwr","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-x81zgwr","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-lt4xpiy","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-lt4xpiy","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"立志欲坚不欲锐，成功在久不在速。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-j20j7nc","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-j20j7nc","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-29p36u9","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-29p36u9","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"赏不逾日，罚不还面。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-8hkizch","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-8hkizch","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-9h1t2n9","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-9h1t2n9","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"布伦南：手头上有点钱的人认为爱是世界上最重要的东西，而穷人则明白世界上最重要的是金钱。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-ra13c1b","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-ra13c1b","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-8lfowbs","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-8lfowbs","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"冯至《十四行集》：我们准备着，深深地领受，那些意想不到的奇迹。在漫长的岁月里，忽然有彗星的出现，狂风乍起。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-e7harys","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-e7harys","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-jv3ski9","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-jv3ski9","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"疾风怒雨，禽鸟戚戚；霁月光风，草木欣欣。天地不可一日无和气，人心不可一日无喜神。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-5of9781","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-5of9781","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-s8t3f8g","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-s8t3f8g","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"丈夫之高华，只在于道德气节。鄙夫之炫耀，但求诸服饰起居。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-k2x4o3o","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-k2x4o3o","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-s0nqr0o","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-s0nqr0o","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"甘井近竭，招木近伐。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-dxri7l9","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-dxri7l9","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-qu7z1kf","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-qu7z1kf","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"善用兵者，屈人之兵而非战也，拔人之城而非攻也，毁人之国而非久也，必以全争于天下。故兵不顿而利可全，此谋攻之法也。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-55roozy","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-55roozy","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-a2axmla","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-a2axmla","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"你吞并一切，像远方，像大海，像时间。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-ygq8hqa","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-ygq8hqa","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-kagkgiq","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-kagkgiq","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"挟取笔端风雨，快写胸中丘壑，不肯下樊笼。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-kpek9j6","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-kpek9j6","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-4gw8wk8","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-4gw8wk8","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"巴尔扎克：一星陨落，黯淡不了星空灿烂；一花凋零，荒芜不了整个春天。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-mygk3st","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-mygk3st","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-x1xzuq2","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-x1xzuq2","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"伯修斯：在所有不幸中，最不幸的事是曾经幸福过。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-f2wweiv","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-f2wweiv","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-srubf7n","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-srubf7n","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"草萤有耀终非火，荷露虽团岂是珠。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-20x9pq3","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-20x9pq3","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-485sr8h","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-485sr8h","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"耳闻之不如目见之，目见之不如足践之。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-hnen9nq","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-hnen9nq","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-s8w0vnn","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-s8w0vnn","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"卖花担上，买得一枝春欲放。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-wuhzjw3","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-wuhzjw3","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-bur9tme","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-bur9tme","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"亭亭山上松，瑟(sè)瑟谷中风。风声一何盛，松枝一何劲。冰霜正惨凄，终岁常端正。岂不罹(lí)凝寒，松柏有本性。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-by22l0j","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-by22l0j","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-o5g3u4i","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-o5g3u4i","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"好问则裕，自用则小。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-qdnm2p7","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-qdnm2p7","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-t3orffh","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-t3orffh","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"雾失楼台，月迷津渡。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-35yip32","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-35yip32","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-06wusgw","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-06wusgw","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"泰戈尔：世界以痛吻我，我也要报之以歌。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-2prxpwp","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-2prxpwp","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-1fbf0ot","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-1fbf0ot","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"千人之诺诺，不如一士之谔谔。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-td8rl6f","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-td8rl6f","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-ckdlboy","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-ckdlboy","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"早岁读书无甚解，晚年省事有奇功。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-2ems91h","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-2ems91h","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-2zd8juv","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-2zd8juv","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"你所浪费的今天，是昨天死去的人奢望的明天；你所厌恶的现在，是未来的你回不去的曾经。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-ny1zx4g","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-ny1zx4g","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-in3g2c9","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-in3g2c9","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"汪国真：有很多人常常抱怨没有机会，其实没有机会本身亦是一个机会：一个锻炼自己耐力和充分积蓄自己力量的机会。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-rl4g3vn","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-rl4g3vn","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-c783rge","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-c783rge","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"世界让我遍体鳞伤，但伤口长出的却是翅膀。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-ild3zgk","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-ild3zgk","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-5r6jrzx","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-5r6jrzx","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"凡战者，以正合，以奇胜。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-zwt7par","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-zwt7par","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-7t4fn86","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-7t4fn86","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"方其中，圆其外。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-fytd1h8","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-fytd1h8","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-io52kzv","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-io52kzv","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"独学而无友，则孤陋而寡闻。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-u4h37j2","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-u4h37j2","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-rq1es3c","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-rq1es3c","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"史铁生：苦难既然把我推到了悬崖的边缘，那么就让我在这悬崖的边缘坐下来，顺便看看悬崖下的流岚雾霭，唱支歌给你听。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-gzzy1ad","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-gzzy1ad","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-ui59k72","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-ui59k72","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"国虽大，好战必亡；天下虽安，忘战必危。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-k0pbvm9","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-k0pbvm9","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-s4fpvf3","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-s4fpvf3","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"加缪：每个冬天的句号都是春暖花开。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-56t4kgm","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-56t4kgm","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-6hhkpro","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-6hhkpro","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"百里趋利，兵家所忌。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-qpsycda","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-qpsycda","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-hcz1ofs","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-hcz1ofs","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"李大钊：谁对时间越吝啬，时间对谁越慷慨。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-d8jitxg","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-d8jitxg","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-oo82l3i","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-oo82l3i","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"粗缯大布裹生涯，腹有诗书气自华。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-yqbsb8m","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-yqbsb8m","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-1d6x1vs","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-1d6x1vs","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"夫未战而庙算胜者，得算多也；未战而庙算不胜者，得算少也。多算胜，少算不胜，而况于无算乎？"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-9sfp72l","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-9sfp72l","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-p6h6zo7","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-p6h6zo7","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"慈不掌兵，情不立事，义不理财，善不为官。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-a68hfwa","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-a68hfwa","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-z1en0s8","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-z1en0s8","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"大巧在所不为，大智在所不虑。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-tabfrx9","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-tabfrx9","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-3oxf16p","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-3oxf16p","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"海到尽头天作岸，山登绝顶我为峰。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-1omzmno","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-1omzmno","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-yb1w9ge","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-yb1w9ge","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"雨之为物，能令昼短，能令夜长。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-y0y79rs","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-y0y79rs","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-ra3xdtb","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-ra3xdtb","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"善出奇者，无穷如天地，不竭如江海。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-27jxg51","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-27jxg51","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-0q01dwb","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-0q01dwb","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"大丈夫行事，当磊磊落落，如日月皎然。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-j1sl4ze","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-j1sl4ze","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-if6acnv","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-if6acnv","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"知者行之始，行者知之成。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-1pcrjmr","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-1pcrjmr","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-8yb9t4o","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-8yb9t4o","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"善用兵者不以短击长，而以长击短。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-om1xks3","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-om1xks3","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-gdkuxdw","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-gdkuxdw","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"振衣千仞冈，濯足万里流。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-gmlo3d0","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-gmlo3d0","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-jc5lswn","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-jc5lswn","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"泰戈尔：你今天受的苦、吃的亏、担的责、扛的罪、忍的痛，到最后都会变成光，照亮你的路。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-u2u8yog","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-u2u8yog","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-y8zb5r7","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-y8zb5r7","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"张而不弛，文武弗能也；弛而不张，文武弗为也。一张一弛，文武之道也。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-7zg56q1","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-7zg56q1","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-q3u5o13","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-q3u5o13","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"善为士者，不武；善战者，不怒；善胜敌者，不与；善用人者，为之下。是谓不争之德，是谓用人之力。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-7xcdzg0","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-7xcdzg0","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-h11jso3","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-h11jso3","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"中心藏之，何日忘之！"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-u0kztqk","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-u0kztqk","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-zeup7k2","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-zeup7k2","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"汪国真：没有比脚更长的路，没有比人更高的山。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-4gbgxhi","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-4gbgxhi","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-be5qv47","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-be5qv47","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"歌德：才能是在寂静中造就，而品格则是在世间汹涌波涛中形成。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-gq2g7tj","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-gq2g7tj","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-vctk8cj","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-vctk8cj","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"我有迷魂招不得，雄鸡一声天下白。少年心事当拏云，谁念幽寒坐呜呃。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-uklz4so","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-uklz4so","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-40hy25c","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-40hy25c","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"尺之木必有节目，寸之玉必有瑕疵。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-fpb4q66","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-fpb4q66","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-27txmpd","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-27txmpd","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"曾国藩：天下古今之庸人，皆以一惰字致败；天下古今之才人，皆以一傲字致败。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-ahw08k5","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-ahw08k5","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-p7ulvum","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-p7ulvum","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"培根：当你孤独寂寞时，阅读可以消遣。当你高谈阔论时，知识可供装饰。当你处世行事时，正确运用知识意味着力量。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-xo8v03o","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-xo8v03o","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-ou5ljij","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-ou5ljij","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"辅车相依，唇亡齿寒。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-32pmjbj","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-32pmjbj","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-28lyuno","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-28lyuno","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"池田大作：荣誉有如萤虫之火，在黑暗的夜空里，它放着光，显示出美丽，极其可贵。但是靠近一看，立刻就会明白它是何等的软弱无力。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-pzd9305","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-pzd9305","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-qe94963","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-qe94963","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"尼采：谁终将声震人间，必长久深自缄默；谁终将点燃闪电，必长久如云漂泊。我的时代还没有到来，有的人死后方生。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-b0zqxc0","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-b0zqxc0","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-3gg3c0x","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-3gg3c0x","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"三毛：梦想，可以天花乱坠；理想，是我们一步一个脚印踩出来的坎坷道路。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-qoxw2za","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-qoxw2za","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-y4w8oy9","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-y4w8oy9","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"志不可一日坠，心不可一日放。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-a0v2of0","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-a0v2of0","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-q4di9b7","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-q4di9b7","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"一双冷眼看世人，满腔热血酬知己。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-oqta04r","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-oqta04r","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-36w58yp","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-36w58yp","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"罗翔：误解是人生常态，理解是稀缺的例外。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-u27y2vp","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-u27y2vp","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-nrkowtn","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-nrkowtn","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"杀人亦有限，列国自有疆。苟能制侵陵，岂在多杀伤。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-lqxs13q","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-lqxs13q","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-q95ja2c","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-q95ja2c","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"朝闻道，夕死可矣。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-w09rewy","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-w09rewy","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-xp2pwcu","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-xp2pwcu","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"丈夫四方志，安可辞固穷。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-wytkk79","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-wytkk79","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-tipwhum","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-tipwhum","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"粪虫至秽变为蝉，而饮露于秋风；腐草无光化为荧，而耀采于夏月。故知洁常自污出，明每从暗生也。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-irczmb5","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-irczmb5","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-c3qcaia","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-c3qcaia","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"物以稀为贵，情因老更慈。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-fzo0e1k","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-fzo0e1k","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-v3dix5w","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-v3dix5w","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"不可积，过不可长。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-nlvfvzr","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-nlvfvzr","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-sjlg8fb","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-sjlg8fb","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"不能受谏，安能谏人。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-uxjk4k9","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-uxjk4k9","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-7nkvve8","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-7nkvve8","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"人生岂草木，寒暑移此心。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-cuim7wl","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-cuim7wl","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-cex21ny","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-cex21ny","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"大丈夫当容人，勿为人所容。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-yumy8j0","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-yumy8j0","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-izj8ffg","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-izj8ffg","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"不为无益之事，何以悦有涯之生。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-926w5fe","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-926w5fe","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-b9458ba","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-b9458ba","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"海棠未雨，梨花先雪。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-323i2ln","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-323i2ln","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-i90kjpm","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-i90kjpm","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"地薄者大木不产，水浅者大鱼不游。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-09yze3h","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-09yze3h","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-vfe9skt","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-vfe9skt","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"忧勤是美德，太苦则无以适性怡情；淡泊是高风，太枯则无以济人利物。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-kdalu55","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-kdalu55","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-hrg6bid","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-hrg6bid","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"读书为身上之用，而人以为纸上之用。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-cl9zdqz","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-cl9zdqz","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-jyfgwhv","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-jyfgwhv","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"天可补，海可填，南山可移。日月既往，不可复追。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-czif8mk","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-czif8mk","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-ngfy0wt","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-ngfy0wt","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"尼布尔：请赐予我平静，去接受我无法改变的；给予我勇气，去改变我能改变的；赐我智慧，分辨这两者的区别。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-pzhnqr5","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-pzhnqr5","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-avy4pir","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-avy4pir","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"腹中贮书一万卷，不肯低头在草莽。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-mul72ad","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-mul72ad","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-sjtjd9j","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-sjtjd9j","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"须知少日拏云志，曾许人间第一流。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-m4vn3o2","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-m4vn3o2","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-t48kpt3","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-t48kpt3","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"时间的步伐有三种：未来姗姗来迟，现在像箭一样飞逝，过去永远静立不动。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-td2gn7k","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-td2gn7k","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-ymzn6vj","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-ymzn6vj","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"天若无雪霜，青松不如草。地若无山川，何人重平道。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-lo9yj3d","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-lo9yj3d","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-co6cakh","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-co6cakh","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"凡心所向，素履所往，生如逆旅，一苇以航。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-0lcx9h6","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-0lcx9h6","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-f0kl5k4","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-f0kl5k4","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"缓事宜急干，敏则有功；急事宜缓办，忙则多错。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-vzhhhb7","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-vzhhhb7","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-lmacxdd","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-lmacxdd","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"众口铄金，积毁销骨。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-s3ip4g9","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-s3ip4g9","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-cpx3qok","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-cpx3qok","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"春日迟迟，卉木萋萋。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-6l0imow","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-6l0imow","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-602u2d1","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-602u2d1","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"若有恒何必三更眠五更起，最无益莫过一日曝十日寒。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-0qf7el7","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-0qf7el7","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-3dwn7xo","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-3dwn7xo","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"百战百胜，非善之善者也；不战而屈人之兵，善之善者也。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-48ho5dj","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-48ho5dj","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-ucmz1v2","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-ucmz1v2","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"人之相知，贵相知心。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-w5y3fqa","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-w5y3fqa","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-511ykwm","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-511ykwm","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"桃李春风一杯酒，江湖夜雨十年灯。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-mgztqsq","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-mgztqsq","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-q5qlocq","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-q5qlocq","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"东风知我欲山行，吹断檐间积雨声。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-49qirq4","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-49qirq4","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-wzqsi34","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-wzqsi34","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"桐花万里丹山路，雏凤清于老凤声。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-njtbrbj","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-njtbrbj","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-71fflye","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-71fflye","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"人生不能设计，你只能面对。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-iytpqgz","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-iytpqgz","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-z649uc1","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-z649uc1","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"天地不仁，以万物为刍狗；圣人不仁，以百姓为刍狗。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-io5urtw","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-io5urtw","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-73bzqhq","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-73bzqhq","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"心随长风去，吹散万里云。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-6xjveun","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-6xjveun","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-w4iop39","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-w4iop39","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"见面怜清瘦，呼儿问苦辛。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-6nr03v0","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-6nr03v0","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-4j1vvmb","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-4j1vvmb","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"查尔斯·A·比尔德：当天空黑暗到一定程度，星辰就会熠熠生辉。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-9uuwmgm","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-9uuwmgm","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-339edae","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-339edae","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"雪中何以赠君别，惟有青青松树枝。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-6mktiap","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-6mktiap","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-lejw58f","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-lejw58f","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"赏必加于有功，刑必断于有罪。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-uruckro","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-uruckro","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-c3f98zy","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-c3f98zy","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"规小节者不能成荣名，恶小耻者不能立大功。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-uhmt090","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-uhmt090","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-6bglghm","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-6bglghm","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"沈从文：聪明人要理解生活，愚蠢人要习惯生活。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-g5bm4nf","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-g5bm4nf","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-ns5lp4m","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-ns5lp4m","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"康德：世界上有两件东西能震撼人们的心灵：一件是我们心中崇高的道德标准；另一件是我们头顶上灿烂的星空。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-p5dovq4","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-p5dovq4","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-173iy0q","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-173iy0q","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"叔本华：财富就像海水，饮得越多，渴得越厉害。名望实际上也是如此。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-guo4ayz","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-guo4ayz","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-kv4jpte","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-kv4jpte","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"兵者，国之大事，死生之地，存亡之道，不可不察也。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-koj7epy","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-koj7epy","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-bhoplph","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-bhoplph","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"兵无常势，水无常形，能因敌变化而取胜者，谓之神。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-r0o5c78","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-r0o5c78","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-icr7i13","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-icr7i13","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"何物动人二月杏花八月桂，有谁催我三更灯火五更鸡。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-scggsvv","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-scggsvv","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-plyo5c9","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-plyo5c9","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"自古骄兵多致败，从来轻敌少成功。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-r9q8n77","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-r9q8n77","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-vkjmu7w","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-vkjmu7w","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"知往日所往之非，则学日进矣；见世人可取者多，则德日进矣。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-c0fnk3c","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-c0fnk3c","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-89rafwi","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-89rafwi","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"马太福音：凡有的，还要加倍给他，叫他有余；没有的，连他剩余的也要夺过来。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-brtzcop","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-brtzcop","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-f5yxqwn","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-f5yxqwn","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"风流不在谈锋胜，袖手无言味最长。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-qsl5vcp","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-qsl5vcp","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-1xt813a","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-1xt813a","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"恻隐之心，人皆有之；羞恶之心，人皆有之；恭敬之心，人皆有之；是非之心，人皆有之。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-1r9rsc5","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-1r9rsc5","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-kgd8ot7","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-kgd8ot7","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"攻人以谋不以力，用兵斗智不斗多。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-x8x4gty","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-x8x4gty","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-w2xq3lk","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-w2xq3lk","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"已识乾坤大，犹怜草木青。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-j2nlos3","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-j2nlos3","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-rpbzgyd","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-rpbzgyd","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"鹏北海，凤朝阳。又携书剑路茫茫。明年此日青云上，却笑人间举子忙。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-jbq2rqt","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-jbq2rqt","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-rc94nqr","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-rc94nqr","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"朝饮木兰之坠露兮，夕餐秋菊之落英。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-b51ncau","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-b51ncau","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-f656izc","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-f656izc","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"千人同心则得千人之力，万人异心则无一人之用。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-k8w4gtp","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-k8w4gtp","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-vky8iwh","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-vky8iwh","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"出其所不趋，趋其所不意。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-fop3uhw","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-fop3uhw","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-lbp1h0l","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-lbp1h0l","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"戒骄风清月朗，除躁海阔天空。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-1cmki6p","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-1cmki6p","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-xze4n67","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-xze4n67","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"何时杖尔看南雪，我与梅花两白头。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-memuw4x","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-memuw4x","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-1e32jh6","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-1e32jh6","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"一时宠利有尽，千秋青史难欺。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-s2k0ory","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-s2k0ory","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-4ed8p9d","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-4ed8p9d","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"山川异域，风月同天。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-vw916s9","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-vw916s9","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-rwimzb1","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-rwimzb1","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"白石似玉，奸佞似贤。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-1kdvlw5","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-1kdvlw5","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-rnr64f0","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-rnr64f0","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"深厚的教养所集成的勇猛，远远胜过无知无情者的鲁莽。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-0ue9ts4","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-0ue9ts4","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-szzqujl","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-szzqujl","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"积财千万，不如薄技在身。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-6q3b5za","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-6q3b5za","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-w3n24hy","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-w3n24hy","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"海明威：生活总是让我们遍体鳞伤，但到后来，那些受伤的地方一定会变成我们最强壮的地方。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-8qxlmgr","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-8qxlmgr","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-t6triii","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-t6triii","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"当年不肯嫁春风，无端却被秋风误。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-cw7lsqx","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-cw7lsqx","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-vgwtseo","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-vgwtseo","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"良辰美景奈何天，赏心乐事谁家院。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-t5w5nmx","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-t5w5nmx","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-og6jj1i","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-og6jj1i","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"唤起一天明月，照我满怀冰雪，浩荡百川流。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-l94zmg1","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-l94zmg1","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-w8k025s","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-w8k025s","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"休对故人思故国，且将新火试新茶。诗酒趁年华。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-5stybjl","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-5stybjl","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-nm9z9au","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-nm9z9au","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"尼采：那些听不见音乐的人，认为那些跳舞的人疯了。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-mrgu84w","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-mrgu84w","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-ezpmdq7","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-ezpmdq7","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"尼采：其实人跟树是一样的，越是向往高处的阳光，它的根就越要伸向黑暗的地底。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-fmku1xw","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-fmku1xw","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-ym3i77g","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-ym3i77g","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"玉可碎而不可改其白，竹可焚而不可毁其节。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-9c28xhr","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-9c28xhr","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-uxnvohf","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-uxnvohf","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"南风吹其心，摇摇为谁吐？"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-32a8erm","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-32a8erm","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-c56gndj","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-c56gndj","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"巴金：希望是人生之需要。人如没有希望，何异江河干涸了流水？"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-ctgr5sr","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-ctgr5sr","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-x0xfjrh","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-x0xfjrh","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"穷不失义，达不离道。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-9rh6aw7","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-9rh6aw7","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-bsj9pcw","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-bsj9pcw","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"为者常成，行者常至。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-j0ecdbs","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-j0ecdbs","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-4jmpmsy","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-4jmpmsy","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"青云当自致，何必求知音？"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-ot80rwm","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-ot80rwm","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-xu5qi9i","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-xu5qi9i","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"争名者于朝，争利者于市。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-mx8vtrf","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-mx8vtrf","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-butbxt5","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-butbxt5","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"天上浮云如白衣，斯须变幻如苍狗。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-mnwbuvg","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-mnwbuvg","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-e0pxza0","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-e0pxza0","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"莺花犹怕春光老，岂可教人枉度春？"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-y0rzg42","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-y0rzg42","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-6wy08z0","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-6wy08z0","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"人生芳秽有千载，世上荣枯无百年。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-bwrzqtz","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-bwrzqtz","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-mipjrfb","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-mipjrfb","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"当你的欢乐和悲哀变大的时候，世界就变小了。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-efex5rs","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-efex5rs","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-gne7f2d","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-gne7f2d","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"故将有五危，必死可杀，必生可虏，忿速可侮，廉洁可辱，爱民可烦。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-z08o3kn","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-z08o3kn","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-ml93gm1","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-ml93gm1","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"纵使文章惊海内，纸上苍生而已。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-bzhv79y","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-bzhv79y","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-i774sva","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-i774sva","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"死生契阔，与子成说。执子之手，与子偕老。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-yskyira","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-yskyira","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-wu0u8h4","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-wu0u8h4","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"兼听则明，偏信则暗。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-vwye48x","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-vwye48x","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-xiyqunr","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-xiyqunr","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"弃燕雀小志，作鸿鹄高翔。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-xtttax9","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-xtttax9","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-syrrs5u","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-syrrs5u","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"眼界要阔，遍历名山大川；度量要宏，熟读五经诸史。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-a80taoy","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-a80taoy","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-i1dll95","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-i1dll95","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"天地存肝胆，江山阅鬓华。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-3wura4m","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-3wura4m","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-ssvsuj9","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-ssvsuj9","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"人生不相见，动如参与商。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-4p10pzb","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-4p10pzb","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-wpd0rh2","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-wpd0rh2","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"莫道君行早，更有早行人。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-cph65gn","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-cph65gn","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-5y09o4s","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-5y09o4s","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"大人者，不失其赤子之心者也。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-3cyzohl","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-3cyzohl","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-nbj080m","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-nbj080m","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"英雄者，胸怀大志，腹有良谋，有包藏宇宙之机，吞吐天地之志者也。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-mgi3nwj","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-mgi3nwj","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-ofadnsl","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-ofadnsl","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"雪里温柔，水边明秀，不借春工力。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-pvle24m","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-pvle24m","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-yethlym","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-yethlym","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"良言一句三冬暖，恶语伤人六月寒。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-lti9yud","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-lti9yud","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-m6wdkaa","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-m6wdkaa","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"学如弓弩，才如箭镞。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-5f0utkw","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-5f0utkw","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-cwbmw26","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-cwbmw26","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"人不读书，其犹夜行。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-pokm9ap","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-pokm9ap","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-l76hbuw","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-l76hbuw","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"穷猿奔林，岂暇择木！"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-y303n4p","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-y303n4p","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-bt9n6i6","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-bt9n6i6","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"令在必信，法在必行。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-55w58lq","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-55w58lq","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-e9capxd","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-e9capxd","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"其疾如风，其徐如林，侵掠如火，不动如山，难知如阴，动如雷震。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-ol1cky8","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-ol1cky8","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-xm81cx6","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-xm81cx6","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"天下熙熙，皆为利来；天下攘攘，皆为利往。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-qpios6p","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-qpios6p","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-w3qxo2i","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-w3qxo2i","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"我亦飘零久！十年来，深恩负尽，死生师友。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-h5f44aw","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-h5f44aw","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-zvheys9","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-zvheys9","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"板凳要坐十年冷，文章不写一句空。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-mgn7v2g","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-mgn7v2g","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-iaq9qbl","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-iaq9qbl","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"有心为善，虽善不赏；无心为恶，虽恶不罚。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-xbbecvh","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-xbbecvh","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-zbkthzk","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-zbkthzk","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"不目见口问，不能尽知也。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-0p4i43y","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-0p4i43y","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-0ar19cy","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-0ar19cy","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"一年之计，莫如树谷；十年之计，莫如树木；终身之计，莫如树人。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-4j566yr","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-4j566yr","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-7pqjtlt","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-7pqjtlt","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"不因幸运而故步自封，不因厄运而一蹶不振。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-nnetvgl","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-nnetvgl","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-azf0va5","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-azf0va5","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"良弓难张，然可以及高入深；良马难乘，然可以任重致远。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-eync1vg","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-eync1vg","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-cf50yt8","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-cf50yt8","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"上兵伐谋，其次伐交，其次伐兵，其下攻城。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-mvqocu8","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-mvqocu8","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-bhpd1cd","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-bhpd1cd","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"志合者不以山海为远，道乖者不以咫尺为近。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-xaj1xj2","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-xaj1xj2","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-oxe8ij9","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-oxe8ij9","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"海水梦悠悠，君愁我亦愁。南风知我意，吹梦到西洲。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-hkaqvf1","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-hkaqvf1","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-a0azszb","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-a0azszb","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"不幸者常常愿意同幸运者相比，抱怨自己的运气。幸运者常常不愿同不幸者相比，相信自己的努力。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-ri4feoe","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-ri4feoe","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-0e3adap","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-0e3adap","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"怯生于勇，弱生于强。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-ih968yn","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-ih968yn","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-p15zqkl","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-p15zqkl","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"贵上极则反贱，贱下极则反贵。贵出如粪土，贱取如珠玉。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-uoly77m","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-uoly77m","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-ymxd3cz","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-ymxd3cz","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"有志者事竟成破釜沉舟百二秦关终属楚，苦心人天不负卧薪尝胆三千越甲可吞吴。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-qepwmd4","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-qepwmd4","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-hpuqen5","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-hpuqen5","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"昔日之得不足以自衿，今日之成不容以自限。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-c2uxs9s","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-c2uxs9s","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-ozvtvqu","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-ozvtvqu","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"不善操舟者，恶河之曲。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-cx5tqme","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-cx5tqme","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-rl7udwu","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-rl7udwu","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"操千曲而后晓声，观千剑而后识器。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-2vds4p5","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-2vds4p5","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-aydrtos","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-aydrtos","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"长安何处在，只在马蹄下。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-yhpgqtq","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-yhpgqtq","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-c1a5coc","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-c1a5coc","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"人情阅尽秋云厚，世事经多蜀道平。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-abomg1t","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-abomg1t","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-hiq1is4","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-hiq1is4","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"志行万里者，不中道而辍足。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-qgbgrov","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-qgbgrov","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-xtaevoo","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-xtaevoo","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"交友须带三分侠气，做人要存一点素心。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-92c9xwg","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-92c9xwg","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-u0pwfgr","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-u0pwfgr","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"男儿不展风云志，空负天生八尺躯。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-t5rhe8z","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-t5rhe8z","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-psswt4j","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-psswt4j","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"愿作远方兽，步步比肩行。愿作深山木，枝枝连理生。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-jvc5uo2","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-jvc5uo2","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-czjvs8o","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-czjvs8o","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"兵不厌诈，将贵知机。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-6g7u0se","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-6g7u0se","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-m5apg60","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-m5apg60","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"上士闻道，勤而行之；中士闻道，若存若亡；下士闻道，大笑之。不笑不足以为道。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-ybjq4yw","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-ybjq4yw","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-xx5hh2w","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-xx5hh2w","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"君子慎始，差若毫厘，缪以千里。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-nr691ba","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-nr691ba","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-osk9y2o","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-osk9y2o","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"古来多被虚名误，宁负虚名身莫负。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-59olwjh","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-59olwjh","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-ojr37r7","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-ojr37r7","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"我志在寥阔，畴昔梦登天。摩挲素月，俯仰已千年。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-74nwj5w","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-74nwj5w","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-qe27n74","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-qe27n74","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"我们每个人出生的时候，并非是两手空空，而是捏了一张生命的借记卡。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-rjiuvqi","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-rjiuvqi","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-g7g8t5f","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-g7g8t5f","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"好风凭借力，送我上青云。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-sp2ecer","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-sp2ecer","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-1ravwpp","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-1ravwpp","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"玉在山而草木润，渊生珠而崖不枯。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-gck1lf2","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-gck1lf2","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-5czlx7d","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-5czlx7d","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"学之染人，甚于丹青。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-ci4fomm","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-ci4fomm","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-m94zkjw","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-m94zkjw","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"天地有万古，此身不再得；人生只百年，此日最易过。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-2sb7vwk","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-2sb7vwk","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-wyxqm9q","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-wyxqm9q","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"十有九人堪白眼，百无一用是书生。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-bsa3c2t","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-bsa3c2t","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-tcwp4o1","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-tcwp4o1","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"丈夫志四海，万里犹比邻。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-pd305r8","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-pd305r8","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-pu33p20","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-pu33p20","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"仗义每多屠狗辈，负心多是读书人。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-qel5ibn","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-qel5ibn","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-argh69c","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-argh69c","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"涓涓不塞，将为江河。荧荧不救，炎炎奈何。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-52e8k8p","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-52e8k8p","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-i7qa306","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-i7qa306","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"人生如寄，多忧何为？今我不乐，岁月如驰。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-rv7cp71","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-rv7cp71","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-ljic2u2","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-ljic2u2","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"天行有常，不为尧存，不为桀亡。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-k1cnmw6","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-k1cnmw6","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-y9dm7kl","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-y9dm7kl","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"读书志在圣贤，非徒科第；为官心存君国，岂计身家？"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-edxlnbr","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-edxlnbr","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-fpuvwd5","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-fpuvwd5","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"少而好学，如日出之阳；壮而好学，如日中之光；老而好学，如秉烛之明。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-ttp8vte","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-ttp8vte","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-emez8wv","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-emez8wv","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"纪伯伦：不要因为走得太远而忘记为什么出发。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-z6idshb","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-z6idshb","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-399f4al","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-399f4al","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"用赏者贵信，用罚者贵必。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-vzoq6ag","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-vzoq6ag","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-f1f81go","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-f1f81go","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"傲不可长，欲不可纵，乐不可极，志不可满。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-htdi2rc","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-htdi2rc","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-sj3v6te","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-sj3v6te","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"君子爱财，取之有道。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-fn04jye","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-fn04jye","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-47p78kp","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-47p78kp","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"余光中：敢在时间里自焚的人，必在永恒里结晶。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-45hupwj","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-45hupwj","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-we1z2qb","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-we1z2qb","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"主不可以怒而兴师，将不可以愠而致战；合于利而动，不合于利而止。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-l22mc2y","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-l22mc2y","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-ztfv8u7","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-ztfv8u7","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"兵形象水，水之形，避高而趋下，兵之形，避实而击虚。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-0bb39qm","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-0bb39qm","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-mape91y","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-mape91y","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"海子：永远是这样，风后面是风，天空上面是天空，道路前面还是道路。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-2j995ci","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-2j995ci","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-0wb83m4","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-0wb83m4","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"史铁生：如果你抑郁了，说明你活在过去；如果你焦虑了，说明你活在未来；如果你平静了，才说明你活在现在。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-1z0le2a","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-1z0le2a","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-e6xy2ul","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-e6xy2ul","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"对愁人勿乐，对哭人勿笑，对失意人勿矜。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-m81c61p","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-m81c61p","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-9yt8ymr","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-9yt8ymr","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"知胜有五：知可以战与不可以战者胜，识众寡之用者胜，上下同欲者胜，以虞待不虞者胜，将能而君不御者胜。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-8g4ebqy","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-8g4ebqy","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-l5fxyq5","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-l5fxyq5","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"钝学累功，不妨精熟。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-dai8qp3","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-dai8qp3","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-de3i3q4","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-de3i3q4","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"闭门即是深山，读书随处净土。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-m8n4zkr","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-m8n4zkr","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-f5o5tk6","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-f5o5tk6","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"人非生而知之者，孰能无惑?惑而不从师，其为惑也，终不解矣。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-cm6jifb","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-cm6jifb","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-qq7ve0k","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-qq7ve0k","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"见胜不过众人之所知，非善之善者也；战胜而天下曰善，非善之善者也。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-9wc2rui","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-9wc2rui","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-pbxo7sk","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-pbxo7sk","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"折芦花赠远，零落一身秋。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-p2g4ttt","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-p2g4ttt","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-lpo2jog","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-lpo2jog","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"老骥伏枥志千里，短锥处囊半寸锋。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-3qc9ebm","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-3qc9ebm","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-ajl94vf","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-ajl94vf","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"只要厄运打不垮信念，希望之光就会驱散绝望之云。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-qugek6v","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-qugek6v","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-ag3ikce","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-ag3ikce","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"以势交者，势尽则疏，以利合者，利尽则散。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-vk88ecy","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-vk88ecy","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-xmyu3iq","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-xmyu3iq","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"如月之恒，如日之升。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-0irkcip","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-0irkcip","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-f8nzgy9","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-f8nzgy9","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"合军聚众，务在激气。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-3xvmcil","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-3xvmcil","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-ouwtgvp","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-ouwtgvp","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"贝尔纳：构成我们学习最大障碍的是已知的东西，而不是未知的东西。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-4mogcl2","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-4mogcl2","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-y1y5470","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-y1y5470","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"约瑟夫·海勒《第二十二条军规》：任何值得为它而死的东西，肯定值得为它而生。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-ddj89ap","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-ddj89ap","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-hftgcm2","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-hftgcm2","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"云路鹏程九万里，雪窗萤火二十年。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-p96bn0g","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-p96bn0g","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-kgppozq","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-kgppozq","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"华而不实，怨之所聚也。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-2eagp04","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-2eagp04","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-caqsd3v","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-caqsd3v","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"精卫衔微木，将以填沧海；刑天舞干戚，猛志固常在。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-59kg891","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-59kg891","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-lnjc5ty","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-lnjc5ty","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"自知者不怨人，知命者不怨天；怨人者穷，怨天者无志。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-bndstv8","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-bndstv8","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-k5l1dhr","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-k5l1dhr","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"丹青不知老将至，富贵于我如浮云。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-64co6fg","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-64co6fg","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-1kgn3x2","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-1kgn3x2","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"胡适：凡富于创造性的人必敏于模仿，凡不善于模仿的人决不能创造。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-oyygq40","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-oyygq40","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-36h6xax","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-36h6xax","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"节义傲青云，文章高白雪。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-26sx47o","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-26sx47o","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-ttjmum5","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-ttjmum5","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"提得起，放得下，算得到，做得完，看得破，撇得开。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-rc65i03","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-rc65i03","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-1fxkk7e","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-1fxkk7e","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"汪曾祺：一定要爱着点什么，恰似草木对光阴的钟情。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-arqrris","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-arqrris","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-auflpw9","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-auflpw9","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"我有所念人，隔在远远乡。我有所感事，结在深深肠。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-wd3vulu","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-wd3vulu","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-9mejlki","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-9mejlki","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"草不谢荣于春风，木不怨落于秋天。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-awm0b6i","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-awm0b6i","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-wq17mw8","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-wq17mw8","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"一竹一兰一石，有节有香有骨。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-d9txmbk","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-d9txmbk","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-1enxbvv","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-1enxbvv","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"笔落惊风雨，诗成泣鬼神。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-zrjiihk","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-zrjiihk","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-ciw7074","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-ciw7074","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"合抱之木，生于毫末；九层之台，起于累土；千里之行，始于足下。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-8r7ad8c","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-8r7ad8c","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-nfcsjzq","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-nfcsjzq","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"山不让尘，川不辞盈。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-27qod7t","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-27qod7t","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-v98to1a","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-v98to1a","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"皑如山上雪，皎若云间月。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-5eii74y","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-5eii74y","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-d9pnl98","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-d9pnl98","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"客子光阴诗卷里，杏花消息雨声中。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-n56ybdg","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-n56ybdg","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-5tjwlcn","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-5tjwlcn","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"尼采：我们的眼睛就是我们的监狱，而目光所及之处就是监狱的围墙。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-ljohsqu","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-ljohsqu","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-wt1gdrm","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-wt1gdrm","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"雪中送炭人间少，锦上添花世上多。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-75tjigl","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-75tjigl","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-p74w9ax","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-p74w9ax","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"蒲柳之姿，望秋而落；松柏之质，经霜弥茂。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-5guyeup","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-5guyeup","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-jl1w4p4","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-jl1w4p4","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"不戚戚于贫贱，不汲汲于富贵。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-r1g56au","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-r1g56au","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-yuh26dn","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-yuh26dn","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"门前红叶地，不扫待知音。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-t5sarze","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-t5sarze","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-ykxi5h1","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-ykxi5h1","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"村上春树：这个世界上根本没有正确的选择，我们只不过是要努力奋斗，使当初的选择变得正确。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-oqtgoyy","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-oqtgoyy","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-2y36x7j","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-2y36x7j","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"缘木求鱼，煎水作冰。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-nu4pso4","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-nu4pso4","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-71g6ivk","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-71g6ivk","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"苟日新，日日新，又日新。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-fw1uk6c","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-fw1uk6c","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-amu0tjm","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-amu0tjm","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"贫无可奈惟求俭，拙亦何妨只要勤。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-nd3ed75","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-nd3ed75","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-zigx8c7","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-zigx8c7","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"文章千古事，得失寸心知。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-2of7z17","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-2of7z17","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-jdv0m4l","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-jdv0m4l","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"雨滴能击穿石头，并不是下落的速度快，而是因为掉落在石头上的次数多。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-96fdnix","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-96fdnix","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-t4nunq9","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-t4nunq9","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"人有逆天之时，天无绝人之路。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-6s8ab4w","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-6s8ab4w","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-lwq542c","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-lwq542c","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"宁为宇宙闲吟客，怕作乾坤窃禄人。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-54x4p7w","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-54x4p7w","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-2hbud1r","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-2hbud1r","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"受光于隙见一床，受光于窗见室央，受光于庭户见一堂，受光于天下照四方。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-5ae35iy","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-5ae35iy","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-5uo6r68","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-5uo6r68","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"马不可以服重，牛不可以追速。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-y9ktlg3","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-y9ktlg3","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-6nwsjp6","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-6nwsjp6","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"改过不吝，从善如流。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-47de58u","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-47de58u","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-a93z5lk","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-a93z5lk","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"虚负凌云万丈才，一生襟抱未曾开。鸟啼花落人何在，竹死桐枯凤不来。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-lgk8of2","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-lgk8of2","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-3h7iz7m","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-3h7iz7m","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"兰生幽谷，不为莫服而不芳；舟在江海，不为莫乘而不浮；君子行义，不为莫知而止休。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-ugmw8ws","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-ugmw8ws","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-tcu5em2","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-tcu5em2","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"一日不思量，也攒眉千度。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-c65h4fu","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-c65h4fu","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-3bhh6lo","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-3bhh6lo","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"彊弩之极，矢不能穿鲁缟；冲风之末，力不能漂鸿毛。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-i08q70u","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-i08q70u","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-8bg7rqf","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-8bg7rqf","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"时来天地皆同力，运去英雄不自由。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-5anvbo6","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-5anvbo6","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-jl0l55s","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-jl0l55s","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"倒持干戈，授人以柄。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-8xg1uiq","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-8xg1uiq","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-fzd3xmq","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-fzd3xmq","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"人生一世，草生一春。来如风雨，去似微尘。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-t71qi5o","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-t71qi5o","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-4d836hh","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-4d836hh","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"雪莱：未来不足惧，过往不须泣。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-xkqz51m","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-xkqz51m","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-tltnga3","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-tltnga3","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"从善如登，从恶如崩。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-j168s6o","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-j168s6o","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-hf8bfgh","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-hf8bfgh","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"春生、夏长、秋收、冬藏，天之正也。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-dtv6fug","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-dtv6fug","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-1amvriy","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-1amvriy","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"前事不忘，后事之师。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-9k0rcys","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-9k0rcys","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-wn2altl","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-wn2altl","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"逢人不说人间事，便是人间无事人。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-mmjvgtm","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-mmjvgtm","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-1thg7c2","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-1thg7c2","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"花开花落树之常，能上能下人中强。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-licrw3a","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-licrw3a","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-jvhl9zg","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-jvhl9zg","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"立品同白玉，读书到青云。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-4ww4355","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-4ww4355","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-hakgquh","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-hakgquh","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"陀思妥耶夫斯基：爱具体的人，不要爱抽象的人。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-k8kfdvp","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-k8kfdvp","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-6hmdrr8","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-6hmdrr8","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"凭君莫话封侯事，一将功成万骨枯。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-tdaxawa","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-tdaxawa","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-jm2rfes","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-jm2rfes","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"天下皆知美之为美，斯恶已。皆知善之为善，斯不善已。有无相生，难易相成，长短相形，高下相盈，音声相和，前后相随，恒也。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-5nopjjc","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-5nopjjc","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-dzeojcc","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-dzeojcc","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"君子之心事，天青日白，不可使人不知；君子之才华，玉韫珠藏，不可使人易知。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-qwi9o8u","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-qwi9o8u","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-ac1vm29","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-ac1vm29","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"除掉荒草的最好办法，不是让除完草的土地荒着，而是种上庄稼。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-nskeqfz","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-nskeqfz","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-yhg26f1","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-yhg26f1","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"善战者，求之于势，不责于人。故能择人而任势。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-hbqvvfv","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-hbqvvfv","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-o1y7eb9","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-o1y7eb9","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"川泽纳污，所以成其深；山岳藏疾，所以就其大。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-de29l91","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-de29l91","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-k0vrru9","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-k0vrru9","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"覆水不可收，行云难重寻。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-fjcvzxw","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-fjcvzxw","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-8z0dnbx","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-8z0dnbx","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"相鼠有皮，人而无仪！人而无仪，不死何为？"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-pj7kluf","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-pj7kluf","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-t9cvhcp","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-t9cvhcp","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"为天地立心，为生民立命，为往圣继绝学，为万世开太平。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-lc69sme","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-lc69sme","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-j9wblnn","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-j9wblnn","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"狡兔死，走狗烹；飞鸟尽，良弓藏；敌国破，谋臣亡。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-0cphgxq","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-0cphgxq","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-ihkozbv","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-ihkozbv","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"马丁·路德·金：我们这一代人终将感到悔恨，不仅仅因为坏人的可憎言行，更因为好人的可怕沉默。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-xsjg75i","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-xsjg75i","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-psewmxi","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-psewmxi","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"我本将心向明月，奈何明月照沟渠。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-bzqjl8f","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-bzqjl8f","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-vuqsipx","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-vuqsipx","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"临渊羡鱼，不如退而结网；扬汤止沸，不如去火抽薪。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-ro78i9m","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-ro78i9m","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-6n5ixl1","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-6n5ixl1","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"芳林新叶催陈叶，流水前波让后波。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-7km20i1","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-7km20i1","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-6qgxpsf","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-6qgxpsf","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"日出扶桑一丈高，人间万事细如毛。野夫怒见不平处，磨损胸中万古刀。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-bmxrpn4","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-bmxrpn4","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-s3iadfd","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-s3iadfd","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"泰戈尔：果实的事业是尊贵的，花的事业是甜美的，但是让我做叶的事业吧，叶是谦逊地、专心地垂着绿荫的。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-bbnd5vo","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-bbnd5vo","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-ect3vsm","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-ect3vsm","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"君子耻不修，不耻见污。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-ch2mvtu","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-ch2mvtu","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-z3re0yf","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-z3re0yf","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"陶行知：做学问就是要学要问。光学不问，只做到一半；光问不学，也只是一半。又学又问，才是完整的学问。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-x5bo6or","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-x5bo6or","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-or27hmu","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-or27hmu","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"恶不可积，过不可长。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-sv8vqna","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-sv8vqna","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-3qzdr17","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-3qzdr17","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"众里嫣然通一顾，人间颜色如尘土。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-dmxzvzr","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-dmxzvzr","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-h9ogkow","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-h9ogkow","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"将者，智、信、仁、勇、严也。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-dpd6yz5","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-dpd6yz5","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-um4aura","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-um4aura","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"老舍：才华是刀刃，辛苦是磨刀石。很锋利的刀刃，若日久不用石磨，也会生锈，成为废物。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-xmwwupz","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-xmwwupz","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-qfmroip","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-qfmroip","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"少年侠气，交结五都雄。肝胆洞，毛发耸。立谈中，死生同。一诺千金重。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-f30adpt","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-f30adpt","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-l7ck8w9","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-l7ck8w9","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"罗曼·罗兰 ：一个人的绝对自由是疯狂，一个国家的绝对自由是混乱。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-4mpwtgz","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-4mpwtgz","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-sncrf5w","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-sncrf5w","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"学然后知不足，教然后知困。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-rr5hps1","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-rr5hps1","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-75f2b7a","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-75f2b7a","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"记人之长，忘人之短。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-1zi4obf","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-1zi4obf","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-srzhbye","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-srzhbye","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"知彼知己者，百战不殆；不知彼而知己，一胜一负，不知彼，不知己，每战必殆。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-na7dtzu","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-na7dtzu","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-pfldh5t","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-pfldh5t","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"月缺不改光，剑折不改刚。月缺魄易满，剑折铸复良。势利压山岳，难屈志士肠。男儿自有守，可杀不可苟。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-rf4lhds","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-rf4lhds","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-ijan2wr","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-ijan2wr","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"人生贵相知，何必金与钱？"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-y4tls6i","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-y4tls6i","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-ehjvh28","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-ehjvh28","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"有真才者，必不矜才。有实学者，必不夸学。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-47p6vyc","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-47p6vyc","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-s0it728","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-s0it728","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"薄我货者也，欲与我市者也；訾我行者，欲与我友者也。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-v0ir6kg","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-v0ir6kg","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-r7llh9c","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-r7llh9c","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"风乍起，吹皱一池春水。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-kuaypaj","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-kuaypaj","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-ne32nad","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-ne32nad","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"人生万事须自为，跬步江山即寥廓。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-20apkm9","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-20apkm9","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-tfixlx3","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-tfixlx3","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"十年磨一剑，霜刃未曾试。今日把示君，谁有不平事？"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-kdl30wq","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-kdl30wq","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-viwxc6b","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-viwxc6b","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"草木秋死，松柏独在。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-ni5ug51","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-ni5ug51","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-17vihf0","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-17vihf0","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"人生是一匹马，轻快而健壮的马。人，要像骑手那样大胆而细心地驾驭它。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-3c2kvmq","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-3c2kvmq","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-fz3lm73","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-fz3lm73","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"水广者鱼大，山高者树修。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-6uvzoen","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-6uvzoen","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-lenmpn8","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-lenmpn8","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"人生如梦，把梦看得太认真，固然是个大傻瓜；但以为人生如梦，就以为不必认真，也是个头等大傻瓜。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-j2fvc89","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-j2fvc89","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-65vuxi2","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-65vuxi2","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"一叶浮萍归大海，为人何处不相逢！"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-ankv8rp","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-ankv8rp","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-5o56jhu","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-5o56jhu","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"力田不如逢年，善仕不如遇合。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-6eo3g5e","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-6eo3g5e","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-ehhhvh8","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-ehhhvh8","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"道路难行钱作马，城池不克酒为兵。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-5u3ftfs","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-5u3ftfs","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-aiii54q","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-aiii54q","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"古人云，“读书百遍，其义自见”。谓读得熟，则不待解说，自晓其义也。余尝谓，读书有三到，谓心到，眼到，口到。心不在此，则眼不看仔细，心眼既不专一，却只漫浪诵读，决不能记，记亦不能久也。三到之中，心到最急。心既到矣，眼口岂不到乎？"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-h2x9wa7","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-h2x9wa7","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-jvwvrt4","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-jvwvrt4","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"知人者智，自知者明。胜人者有力，自胜者强。知足者富。强行者有志。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-ra305ca","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-ra305ca","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-pozq36r","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-pozq36r","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"驿寄梅花，鱼传尺素。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-k620h9z","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-k620h9z","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-uv8b6km","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-uv8b6km","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"自然既极博大，也极残忍，战胜一切，孕育众生。蝼蚁蚍蜉，伟人巨匠，一样在它怀抱中，和光同见。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-i1ijchy","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-i1ijchy","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-8wz8ut9","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-8wz8ut9","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"尼采：与恶龙缠斗过久，自身亦成恶龙；凝视深渊过久，深渊将回以凝视。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-d778uuz","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-d778uuz","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-xskpy32","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-xskpy32","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"天戴其苍，地履其黄，纵有千古，横有八荒，前途似海，来日方长。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-luwrvux","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-luwrvux","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-wkns2sa","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-wkns2sa","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"君子坦荡荡，小人长戚戚。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-h9ohq8i","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-h9ohq8i","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-pkrelm0","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-pkrelm0","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"心中有丘壑，眉目作山河。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-ayp81es","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-ayp81es","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-nqbyodc","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-nqbyodc","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"寄蜉蝣于天地，渺沧海之一粟。哀吾生之须臾，羡长江之无穷。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-9ykcg9h","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-9ykcg9h","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-wprilpn","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-wprilpn","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"明代思想家袁了凡：昨日种种，譬如昨日死；今日种种，譬如今日生。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-a3jlbxd","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-a3jlbxd","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-9y8u375","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-9y8u375","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"黑格尔：只有永远躺在泥坑里的人，才不会再掉进坑里。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-0wgvs7j","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-0wgvs7j","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-90ww7z7","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-90ww7z7","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"子在齐闻《韶》，三月不知肉味，曰：‘不图为乐之至于斯也。’"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-50p1jbf","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-50p1jbf","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-8952leu","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-8952leu","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"史铁生：命定的局限尽可永在，不屈的挑战却不可须臾或缺。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-r0g48jo","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-r0g48jo","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-63xhtjc","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-63xhtjc","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"汪国真：当我走向你的时候，我原想收获一缕春风，你却给了我整个春天。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-zkk8t80","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-zkk8t80","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-u6k2to5","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-u6k2to5","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"泰戈尔：我相信，在群星当中有一颗星星，引领我的生命，穿越不可知的黑暗。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-o5k624j","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-o5k624j","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-pq2xelz","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-pq2xelz","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"汪国真：心晴的时候，雨也是晴；心雨的时候，晴也是雨。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-bca56m3","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-bca56m3","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-gy65ti8","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-gy65ti8","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"聂卫平：遇到顺势而下的时候，就一泻千里；遇到阻碍过不去的时候，就绕一下，但我的目标一直是向前走的。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-c4gh1jx","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-c4gh1jx","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-xcydvaj","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-xcydvaj","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"曼德拉：我没有失败过。要么赢得胜利，要么学到东西。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-xrizbwi","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-xrizbwi","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-8wzwfdh","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-8wzwfdh","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"时间是单程车票，我们只能向前；而记忆是随身行李，始终伴你同行。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-j09nyig","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-j09nyig","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-hfge8v1","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-hfge8v1","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"喷泉之所以漂亮，是因为它有压力；瀑布之所以壮观，是因为它没有退路；滴水之所以能穿石，是因为它贵在坚持。一只站在树枝上的鸟，从不害怕树枝会断裂，因为它相信的不是树枝，而是它自己的翅膀。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-gmdlekw","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-gmdlekw","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-t3xewrt","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-t3xewrt","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"追风赶月莫停留，平芜尽处是春山。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-z9ue23u","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-z9ue23u","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-ukzxyth","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-ukzxyth","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"苏轼《浣溪沙·游蕲水清泉寺》"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-ei7ao2m","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-ei7ao2m","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-y00c669","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-y00c669","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"朱敦儒《鹧鸪天·西都作》"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-jrvd8mk","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-jrvd8mk","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-rcfr3xi","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-rcfr3xi","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"杜甫《蜀相》"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-bk21j4t","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-bk21j4t","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-zue08ny","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-zue08ny","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"李白《忆秦娥》"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-sodk6e7","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-sodk6e7","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-qmy8t5n","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-qmy8t5n","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"李白《上李邕》"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-diitk9r","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-diitk9r","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-vk3k2nt","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-vk3k2nt","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"陆游《金错刀行》"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-c4ugu2d","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-c4ugu2d","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-usuo0bv","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-usuo0bv","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"李煜《虞美人》"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-8h4kxtc","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-8h4kxtc","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-tk104ds","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-tk104ds","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"白居易《琵琶行》"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-guu0upw","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-guu0upw","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-l4ixw5p","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-l4ixw5p","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"礼记《大学》"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-be14z4w","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-be14z4w","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-qwsx0rs","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-qwsx0rs","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"范仲淹《岳阳楼记》"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-l56olef","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-l56olef","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-24e8bqa","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-24e8bqa","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"张若虚《春江花月夜》"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-aszoswd","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-aszoswd","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-872vo6e","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-872vo6e","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"李白《侠客行》"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-0l3wznx","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-0l3wznx","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605081425-ljfbaph","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605081425-ljfbaph","updated":"20260605081425"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"诗经《无衣》"}]}]},{"ID":"20260605081425-fzxpwbg","